caption.p: Food consumption in female offspring at 7 months of age. Estimated marginal means ( ±) SEM of food intake at 7 months of age in 12 h increments of both light and dark cycle ( n = 7, 4, 6, 6, 5 respectively for vehicle, 1.5, 15, 150, and 1,500 μg/kg/day treatment groups). * p < 0.05 relative to vehicle. Models included date of recording as a covariate.
